00:47:45,487 --> 00:47:47,239
of this year's Best Managed Company Award.

497
00:47:48,448 --> 00:47:51,952
The Almighty is finally rewarding me for
my hard work.

498
00:47:53,495 --> 00:47:55,205
This award will help us

499
00:47:55,289 --> 00:47:58,041
