00:48:17,978 --> 00:48:21,607
You said it yourself that you'd make sure
this project became a success.

506
00:48:21,690 --> 00:48:23,775
Do you think running a company is a joke?

507
00:48:30,115 --> 00:48:31,867
There's something you're ignoring.

508
00:48:34,911 --> 00:48:36,371
You can deny it all you want,

509
00:48:37,456 --> 00:48:38,874
but you are still my son.

510
00:49:24,836 --> 00:49:26,004
Let's meet now.

511
00:49:47,317 --> 00:49:49,027
Considering how serious your injury was,

512
00:49:49,820 --> 00:49:51,071
you seem to be doing all right.

