00:49:57,869 --> 00:49:59,413
Why are you so upset?

516
00:50:01,081 --> 00:50:02,749
Because I dropped the honorifics?

517
00:50:03,291 --> 00:50:05,627
Or is it because I'm telling the truth?

518
00:50:29,901 --> 00:50:30,944
I understand.

519
00:50:31,653 --> 00:50:34,114
She was your first love,
for goodness' sake.

520
00:50:35,449 --> 00:50:37,033
It was an unfortunate accident.

521
00:50:38,410 --> 00:50:40,579
You wanted to save her,
so you called it in yourself.

522
00:50:40,662 --> 00:50:43,206
But she died,
and you didn't want to go to jail,

523
00:50:43,290 --> 00:50:44,916
so you hid it all this time.

524
00:50:46,126 --> 00:50:48,545
Now that you're becoming a father,

525
00:50:48,628 --> 00:50:50,922
I bet you want to
conceal it more thoroughly.

526
00:50:54,217 --> 00:50:55,510
Are you done talking?

527
00:51:02,601 --> 00:51:04,644
When you told me
that Jeong-won was pregnant,

528
00:51:04,728 --> 00:51:05,812
you said this to me.

529
00:51:07,814 --> 00:51:10,984
I don't want her to suffer
any pain or hardship.

530
00:51:11,651 --> 00:51:12,903
That's why I'd like you

531
00:51:14,237 --> 00:51:16,448
to set her free.

532
00:51:16,531 --> 00:51:19,785
Help her so she doesn't have to suffer.

533
00:51:21,077 --> 00:51:24,289
You needed to hear those words
more than I did.

534
00:51:27,125 --> 00:51:29,252
In the past, I was sure
your feelings for Jeong-won

535
00:51:31,087 --> 00:51:33,757
were caused by
your obsession with her, not love.

536
00:51:34,925 --> 00:51:36,051
But that day,

537
00:51:36,968 --> 00:51:38,929
after hearing what you said, I realized

538
00:51:42,265 --> 00:51:43,350
that it was love after all.

539
00:51:50,232 --> 00:51:51,316
By keeping this up,

540
00:51:52,734 --> 00:51:54,820
you will only make Jeong-won suffer more.

541
00:51:57,781 --> 00:51:58,740
So give up already.

542
00:52:26,935 --> 00:52:27,769
INCORRECT PASSWORD

543
00:52:39,614 --> 00:52:41,199
Do I have to give up like this?

544
00:52:56,131 --> 00:52:58,550
I'm keeping it in a safe place
just in case.

545
00:52:58,633 --> 00:53:00,552
Even if something happens to me,

546
00:53:00,635 --> 00:53:04,681
that evidence
will never be found or disappear.

547
00:53:07,559 --> 00:53:09,477
The fact that Dad was so sure

548
00:53:10,145 --> 00:53:13,440
probably means it won't be found
even if it was hacked.

549
00:53:14,691 --> 00:53:16,276
Was there a different ID?

550
00:53:48,892 --> 00:53:49,893
DECEMBER 24, 2009

551
00:54:52,205 --> 00:54:53,999
Meet me at the place where we first met.

552
00:54:54,833 --> 00:54:55,834
I'll wait for you.

553
00:55:26,406 --> 00:55:27,449
Jeong-won.

554
00:55:28,658 --> 00:55:29,951
Why did you want to meet here?

555
00:55:32,120 --> 00:55:33,413
The day we first met,

556
00:55:35,623 --> 00:55:36,708
you were…

557
00:55:38,209 --> 00:55:39,794
staring at the waves.

558
00:55:44,841 --> 00:55:45,842
That's right.

559
00:55:47,510 --> 00:55:49,262
Meeting you here that day…

560
00:55:51,222 --> 00:55:52,766
felt like a miracle.

561
00:55:59,939 --> 00:56:01,107
Jeong-won.

562
00:56:04,778 --> 00:56:06,404
-What's wrong?
-Woo-jae.

563
00:56:07,614 --> 00:56:08,656
I know everything.

564
00:56:10,200 --> 00:56:11,326
I saw everything.

565
00:56:13,912 --> 00:56:16,915
The videos of the accident my father took.

566
00:56:20,627 --> 00:56:21,669
I found them.

567
00:56:32,597 --> 00:56:33,807
Why did you do that?

568
00:56:35,183 --> 00:56:36,643
Why did you do that? Why?

569
00:56:38,645 --> 00:56:41,064
How could you kill someone?

570
00:56:42,023 --> 00:56:43,024
How?

571
00:57:02,043 --> 00:57:03,128
Jeong-won.

572
00:57:05,547 --> 00:57:06,798
What do I do?

573
00:57:08,675 --> 00:57:10,218
I really deserve to die.

574
00:57:13,429 --> 00:57:14,764
Kill me, please.

575
00:57:24,732 --> 00:57:26,317
Before I met you…

576
00:57:30,155 --> 00:57:32,157
I should have just died here.

577
00:57:35,118 --> 00:57:37,328
I regret getting you roped into my life.

578
00:57:41,583 --> 00:57:42,625
Jeong-won.

579
00:57:44,711 --> 00:57:46,045
I know. I…

580
00:57:49,632 --> 00:57:51,176
I know I'm a horrible person.

581
00:57:55,513 --> 00:57:59,100
Before you turn into a horrible person,
you must stop here.

582
00:58:00,143 --> 00:58:01,519
You have to stop.

583
00:58:02,270 --> 00:58:03,313
Look at me.

584
00:58:04,105 --> 00:58:05,148
Look at me.

585
00:58:07,358 --> 00:58:10,487
You're the only one
who can reveal the truth.

586
00:58:12,530 --> 00:58:13,615
My dad…

587
00:58:15,033 --> 00:58:16,743
Your father killed him, didn't he?

588
00:58:24,209 --> 00:58:25,418
I'm sorry.

589
00:58:28,004 --> 00:58:29,506
I'm really sorry.

590
00:58:36,012 --> 00:58:38,014
I'm so sorry.

591
00:58:45,396 --> 00:58:47,899
I'm sorry.

592
00:59:00,495 --> 00:59:01,996
Until just now,

593
00:59:03,748 --> 00:59:07,085
I felt as though it'd swallow us.

594
00:59:11,422 --> 00:59:12,465
Let's…

595
00:59:14,592 --> 00:59:15,593
just go.

596
00:59:16,261 --> 00:59:17,554
Let's go to the police station.

597
00:59:22,475 --> 00:59:23,935
Make the right choice.

598
00:59:24,727 --> 00:59:25,937
I will go with you.

599
00:59:28,731 --> 00:59:30,984
Before you found out about what I did,

600
00:59:31,651 --> 00:59:34,571
I kept getting conflicting thoughts
throughout the day.

601
00:59:35,989 --> 00:59:38,074
"Shall I just tell her everything?"

602
00:59:38,783 --> 00:59:40,994
"Or shall I hide somewhere alone?"

603
00:59:46,958 --> 00:59:48,459
But you've found out…

604
00:59:51,379 --> 00:59:52,463
so it's all over.

605
00:59:55,508 --> 00:59:56,718
I've let it all go.

606
01:00:00,388 --> 01:00:02,765
I'll do the one last thing I can…

607
01:00:05,393 --> 01:00:07,103
and accept punishment for what I did.

608
01:00:14,152 --> 01:00:16,779
THE 20TH MANAGEMENT AWARDS

609
01:00:16,863 --> 01:00:19,741
The 20th Management Awards.

610
01:00:19,824 --> 01:00:22,994
A number of companies
have received awards today.

611
01:00:23,077 --> 01:00:26,372
Now, the only award remaining

612
01:00:26,456 --> 01:00:29,375
is the Grand Award.

613
01:00:29,459 --> 01:00:32,503
I will now announce the winner.

614
01:00:33,838 --> 01:00:35,048
All right.

615
01:00:35,131 --> 01:00:38,009
This year's Grand Award goes to

616
01:00:39,177 --> 01:00:41,512
Mujin Group. Congratulations.

617
01:00:42,597 --> 01:00:45,308
MUJIN GROUP

618
01:00:57,862 --> 01:01:01,115
"You were chosen as
the recipient of the Grand Award

619
01:01:01,199 --> 01:01:04,494
for your continuous research
and development efforts

620
01:01:04,577 --> 01:01:06,663
which have contributed to
stimulating competition

621
01:01:06,746 --> 01:01:08,289
in the industry's economic growth

622
01:01:08,373 --> 01:01:11,584
while dutifully carrying out your
social responsibilities as a company."

623
01:01:44,784 --> 01:01:46,035
I am…

624
01:01:47,995 --> 01:01:49,080
a murderer.

625
01:01:53,751 --> 01:01:55,962
On December 24, 2009,

626
01:01:57,380 --> 01:01:59,966
I was responsible for a hit-and-run
and killed someone.

627
01:02:02,301 --> 01:02:04,095
-What?
-What is he saying?

628
01:02:15,732 --> 01:02:17,150
Then…

629
01:02:18,776 --> 01:02:22,488
my father buried the body in Mueonsan.

630
01:03:12,747 --> 01:03:15,792
Chairman Seol will use
Seol Woo-jae's mental health records

631
01:03:15,875 --> 01:03:18,002
and his drug use
to render his statement inadmissible.

632
01:03:18,085 --> 01:03:20,421
How dare you use my son?

633
01:03:20,505 --> 01:03:22,048
Father, you will crumble.

634
01:03:22,131 --> 01:03:23,591
I will make it happen.

635
01:03:23,674 --> 01:03:25,092
Don't think about anything else.

636
01:03:25,176 --> 01:03:26,385
Just do what you need to do.

637
01:03:26,469 --> 01:03:28,012
Only you can do it.

638
01:03:28,095 --> 01:03:31,015
Why don't we use the media?

639
01:03:31,098 --> 01:03:33,184
Jeong-won, I have a favor to ask.

640
01:03:33,851 --> 01:03:35,645
Finally, I can see the end.

641
01:03:35,728 --> 01:03:39,023
I can end my misery
by ending things with you on good terms.

642
01:03:39,106 --> 01:03:40,566
Do as you please,

643
01:03:40,650 --> 01:03:44,570
but I'll always think of you,
and I'll wait for you.

